After creating your account, you'll be guided through a streamlined onboarding process to set up your profile, create your team, and select a billing plan.

## Onboarding Flow

The onboarding process consists of three quick steps to get you started:

### Step 1: Profile Information

Enter your basic profile information:

1. **Your Name** - Enter your full name
2. Click **Continue** to proceed

This is how you'll appear to your teammates and throughout the application.

### Step 2: Team Setup

Create your team workspace:

1. **Team Name** - Enter a name for your team
2. Click **Continue** to proceed

Your team name will be used to create a unique team workspace where you can collaborate with team members. A URL-friendly slug will be automatically generated from your team name.

### Step 3: Plan Selection

Choose the billing plan that works best for your team:

1. Review the available pricing plans
2. Select the plan that fits your needs
3. Click on your chosen plan to proceed to checkout

After selecting a plan, you'll be taken to an embedded checkout where you can complete your payment setup.

## Completing Onboarding

After completing the checkout process:

1. You'll be redirected to a completion screen
2. The system will finalize your account setup (this takes a few seconds)
3. You'll see "Setting up your account..." while we prepare your workspace
4. Once complete, you'll be automatically redirected to your home page

